## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of Disney's strategies and innovations. Some sources may have a limited scope or focus on specific elements of Disney's operations. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of the media and entertainment industry means that new developments may not be fully captured in this report.